                Theory of Formal Languages
                University of Massachusetts Boston
                Spring 2015

INTRODUCTION

    This repository contains the source code developed for Theory of
    Formal Languages course at University of Massachusetts Boston. It
    includes solutions to three assignments.

BUILDING

    The package(s) needed for building source code on ubuntu trusty
    platform are listed below.

        - texlive-latex-base
        - texlive-latex-extra
        - texlive-latex3
        - pgf
        - ghostscript

    Once you have all packages, all you need is `make` to produce all
    documents.

CONTRIBUTION

    Content of this repository is not subject to change. Bug reports
    however are appreciated.

